Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:14.31,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}独自一人时便会听到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:20.16,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}如果痛苦放弃也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:25.06,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}那如同黑洞般深邃
